    Location: 0x0000000000005510, Base: 0x0000000000000000, Semaphore: 0x0000000000000008
    Arguments: -4@[sp, 4]
  ...
  stapsdt              0x00000032       NT_STAPSDT (SystemTap probe descriptors)
    Provider: test
